      "message": "By a lot, yes! 13.5ms -\u003e 5.1. And those 5.1ms are actually higher up in the Ganesh stack where there are a lot of potential optimizations, not in tessellation.\n\nAt this point it looks like Skia won\u0027t become the bottleneck until JS is 2x faster (hopefully soon 🙃), and the GPU won\u0027t become the bottleneck until Skia is 4.5x faster and JS is 9x faster.",
